{"type":null,"faqId":47455,"title":"Why can't my phone connect to a router over Wi-Fi?","answer":" <p style=\"margin: 4pt 0in 4pt 106.3pt; line-height: 12pt; text-indent: -21.25pt; font-size: 10.5pt; -ms-layout-grid-mode: char; tab-stops: list 106.3pt;\">  <br>\n <font face=\"Arial\"> <span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">\n </span> </font> </p>\n <font face=\"Arial\"> <span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">\n </span> </font>\n <p> <font face=\"Arial\"> <span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">  </span> <span style=\"color: black; font-size: 10.5pt;\">1.  </span> <span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">  </span> <span style=\"color: black; font-size: 7pt;\"> <span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">  </span> <span style=\"font-size: 9pt;\"> <span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;  </span> </span> <span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">  </span> </span> <span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">  </span> <span style=\"color: black; font-size: 10.5pt;\">If the Wi-Fi hotspot is encrypted, check whether the password you\nentered is correct. Note that the password is case-sensitive.  </span> <span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">  </span> </font> </p>\n <font face=\"Arial\"> <span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">\n </span> </font>\n <p style=\"margin: 4pt 0cm; line-height: 12pt; font-size: 12pt; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"> <font face=\"Arial\"> <span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">  </span> <span style=\"color: black; font-size: 10.5pt;\">2.  </span> <span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">  </span> <span style=\"color: black; font-size: 10.5pt;\">   </span> <span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">  </span> <span style=\"color: black; font-size: 10.5pt;\">Check whether the Wi-Fi hotspot name or password has changed. If\nso, obtain the new information and try again.  </span> <span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">  </span> </font> </p>\n <font face=\"Arial\"> <span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">\n </span> </font>\n <p style=\"margin: 4pt 0cm; line-height: 12pt; font-size: 12pt; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"> <font face=\"Arial\"> <span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">  </span> <span style=\"color: black; font-size: 10.5pt;\">3.  </span> <span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">  </span> <span style=\"color: black; font-size: 10.5pt;\">   </span> <span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">  </span> <span style=\"color: black; font-size: 10.5pt;\">Make sure you are within the working range of the Wi-Fi hotspot;\notherwise the Wi-Fi connection will automatically disconnect.  </span> <span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">  </span> </font> </p>\n <font face=\"Arial\"> <span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">\n </span> </font>\n <p style=\"margin: 4pt 0cm; line-height: 12pt; font-size: 12pt; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"> <font face=\"Arial\"> <span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">  </span> <span style=\"color: black; font-size: 10.5pt;\">4.  </span> <span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">  </span> <span style=\"color: black; font-size: 7pt;\"> <span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">  </span> <span style=\"font-size: 9pt;\"> <span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;  </span> </span> <span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">  </span> </span> <span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">  </span> <span style=\"color: black; font-size: 10.5pt;\">The number of connected devices may have\nreached the Wi-Fi hotspot's limit. Try connecting to another available network.  </span> <span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">  </span> </font> </p>\n <font face=\"Arial\"> <span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">\n </span> </font>\n <p style=\"margin: 4pt 0cm; line-height: 12pt; font-size: 12pt; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"> <font face=\"Arial\"> <span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">  </span> <span style=\"color: black; font-size: 10.5pt;\">5.  </span> <span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">  </span> <span style=\"color: black; font-size: 7pt;\"> <span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">  </span> <span style=\"font-size: 9pt;\"> <span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;  </span> </span> <span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">  </span> </span> <span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">  </span> <span style=\"color: black; font-size: 10.5pt;\">If your phone can't connect to the Wi-Fi\nhotspot and keeps obtaining an IP address, set a static IP address for it as follows:  </span> <span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">  </span> </font> </p>\n <font face=\"Arial\"> <span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">\n </span> </font>\n <p style=\"margin: 8pt 0cm; line-height: 12pt; font-size: 12pt; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"> <font face=\"Arial\"> <span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">  </span> <span style=\"color: black; font-size: 10.5pt;\">For an encrypted Wi-Fi hotspot, touch the hotspot name on the\nWi-Fi settings screen.  </span> <span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">  </span> </font> </p>\n <font face=\"Arial\"> <span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">\n </span> </font>\n <p style=\"margin: 8pt 0cm; line-height: 12pt; font-size: 12pt; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"> <font face=\"Arial\"> <span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">  </span> <span style=\"color: black; font-size: 10.5pt;\"> <span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">  </span> <span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">In the displayed dialog box, select  </span> <span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">  </span> <span -converted-space=\"\"> <span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">  </span> <span style=\"font-size: 9pt;\"> <span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;  </span> </span> <span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">  </span> </span> <span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">  </span> <b> <span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">  </span> <span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">Show advanced options  </span> <span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">  </span> </b> <span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">  </span> <span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">. Under  </span> <span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">  </span> <span -converted-space=\"\"> <span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">  </span> <span style=\"font-size: 9pt;\"> <span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;  </span> </span> <span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">  </span> </span> <span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">  </span> <b> <span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">  </span> <span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">IP settings  </span> <span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">  </span> </b> <span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">  </span> <span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">, touch the\ndrop-down list box and select  </span> <span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">  </span> <span style=\"font-size: 9pt;\"> <span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;  </span> </span> <span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">  </span> </span> <span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">  </span> <b> <span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">  </span> <span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">Static  </span> <span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">  </span> </b> <span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">  </span> <span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">.\nThen enter the IP address and domain name. Enter the password and touch  </span> <span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">  </span> <span -converted-space=\"\"> <span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">  </span> <span style=\"font-size: 9pt;\"> <span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;  </span> </span> <span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">  </span> </span> <span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">  </span> <b> <span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">  </span> <span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">Connect  </span> <span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">  </span> </b> <span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">  </span> </font> <span style=\"font-size: 9pt;\"> <font face=\"Arial\"> <span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">. </span> </font> <span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">  </span> </span> <span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">  </span> <br>\n </p>\n <p>  </p>\n <p>  <img border=\"0\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=SupportImage&imagePath=/20151019112729945001.png\">  <br>\n </p>\n <p> <font face=\"Arial\">For an open Wi-Fi hotspot, on the Wi-Fi settings screen, touch and hold the hotspot name. In the displayed option menu, select   <b>Modify network  </b>. In the displayed dialog box, select   <b>Show advanced options  </b>. Under   <b>IP settings  </b>, touch the drop-down list box and select   <b>Static  </b>. Then enter the IP address and domain name. After a connection is set up, a Wi-Fi icon will be displayed on the status bar. </font>  </p>\n <p>  <img border=\"0\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=SupportImage&imagePath=/20151019112801561001.png\">  <img border=\"0\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=SupportImage&imagePath=/20151019112811921001.png\">  </p>\n <p>\n <p style=\"margin: 4pt 0cm; line-height: 12pt; font-size: 12pt; tab-stops: list 106.3pt;\">  <span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">  <font face=\"Arial\"> <span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">1.  </span> <span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">  </span> <span style=\"font-size: 7pt;\"> <span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">  </span> <span style=\"font-size: 9pt;\"> <span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;  </span> </span> <span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">  </span> </span> <span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">  </span> <span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">Check\nwhether the MAC address filtering is enabled on your wireless router. If yes,\nphones not in the list can't connect to the Wi-Fi hotspot. For details about\nconfiguring the router, see the router User Guide.  </span> <span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">  </span> </font> </span> <font face=\"Arial\"> <span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">  </span> </font> </p>\n <font face=\"Arial\"> <span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">\n </span> </font>\n <p style=\"margin: 4pt 0cm; line-height: 12pt; font-size: 12pt; -ms-layout-grid-mode: char; tab-stops: list 106.3pt;\"> <font face=\"Arial\"> <span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">  </span> <span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"> <span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">  </span> <span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">2.  </span> <span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">  </span> <span style=\"font-size: 7pt;\"> <span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">  </span> <span style=\"font-size: 9pt;\"> <span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;  </span> </span> <span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">  </span> </span> <span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">  </span> <span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">To\nconnect to some public Wi-Fi hotspots, you may need to log in to a web page for\nregistration. For details, contact the Wi-Fi hotspot provider.  </span> <span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">  </span> </span> <span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">  </span> </font> </p>\n <font face=\"Arial\"> <span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">\n </span> </font>\n <p style=\"margin: 8pt 0cm; line-height: 12pt; font-size: 12pt; -ms-layout-grid-mode: char; punctuation-trim: leading;\"> <font face=\"Arial\"> <span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">  </span> </font> <span style=\"font-size: 9pt;\"> <font face=\"Arial\"> <span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">If\nthe problem persists, restart the Wi-Fi on your phone or restart the Wi-Fi\nhotspot device. </span> </font> <span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">  </span> </span>  </p>\n <br>\n <p>  </p>\n <p>&nbsp;  </p>","faqTypeId":null,"faqType":null,"useful":7,"unUseful":9,"languageId":242,"languageName":"id","faqCode":"2963","faqTypeCode":null,"isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1445225298000,"seriesProductName":"RIO-L01","visitedTimes":3105,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":null,"avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}